This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Boström, Sven, Holovachov, Oleksandr (2019): Descriptions of species of Acrobeles von Linstow, 1877 (Nematoda, Rhabditida, Cephalobidae) from Kelso Dunes, Mojave National Preserve, California, USA.
